-- Safran Isn't Considering Hostile Takeover on Zodiac, La Tribune Reports
-- Albertina Torsoli
-- 2010-07-13T04:44:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/safran-isn-t-considering-hostile-takeover-on-zodiac-la-tribune-reports.html

          
          
             Safran SA is not considering a
hostile takeover on Zodiac Aerospace SA, French daily La Tribune
said, citing comments by Jean-Pierre Cojan, who heads Safran’s
strategy and development. Safran “is not at this stage”
considering to go hostile, Cojan said, according to La Tribune.
Safran “took act” of Zodiac’s rejection of its offer but will
press further with the project, Cojan also said, according to
the newspaper.  
          
          


  


        